title: Persistant Street Solicitor
description:
Written by Zack Phillips
Starring: Langan Kingsley, Dan Hodapp, James McCarthy, Kerry O'Brien, Alene Latimer, Jon Bershad

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, June 3, 2013.

Filmed by Tom Levin, Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
